<section class="features-section">
    <h2>Library Features</h2>

    <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Available Books</h3>
            <p>Members can browse available books with title, author, genre, ISBN and availability status.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Most Borrowed Books</h3>
            <p>The system can display popular books based on borrowing records.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>New Arrivals</h3>
            <p>Newly added books can be shown on the homepage for members.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Library Services</h3>
            <p>Users can access borrowing, reservations, feedback, login and registration services.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>